OL,3,CRAF veteran Derrick Grubb celebrates
OL,4,C100 years of his 'good life'
OL,6,FA retired Royal Air Force squadron
OL,7,Fleader has spoken about how he has had
OL,8,Fa "good life" and enjoyed his time in
OL,9,Fthe services as he celebrated his
OL,10,F100th birthday.
OL,12,FA party was held for Derrick Grubb, of
OL,13,F, Hampshire, on Monday by the Veterans
OL,14,FGroup which meets at the Rowans
OL,15,FHospice's Living Well Centre in
OL,16,FWaterlooville, to mark his milestone
OL,17,Fbirthday.
