OL,3,CRAF veteran Derrick Grubb celebrates
OL,4,C100 years of his 'good life'
OL,6,FWhen asked about the secret of his
OL,7,Flong life, Mr Grubb, whose birthday
OL,8,Fwas on April 12, said: "I don't know,
OL,9,FI've had a good life, I haven't had
OL,10,Fany bad ills in my life and I haven't
OL,11,Fbeen in hospital apart from a minor
OL,12,Foperation and I was only there two
OL,13,Fdays.
OL,15,F"I've thoroughly enjoyed my service
OL,16,Flife, I enjoyed it so much I wrote a
OL,17,Fbook about it.
