OL,3,CRAF veteran Derrick Grubb celebrates
OL,4,C100 years of his 'good life'
OL,6,F"I trained as a pilot and got shot
OL,7,Fdown in operations over Italy and
OL,8,Fspent a year in a prisoner of war camp
OL,9,Fand when I came back, they asked me
OL,10,Fwhat I wanted to do, I said 'fly'.
OL,12,F"So I signed up for four years and
OL,13,Fduring those four years they asked me
OL,14,Fif I wanted to be commissioned and I
OL,15,Fserved all in all for 34 years.
OL,17,F"It was all so enjoyable I wrote about
OL,18,Fmy life in the air force."
